== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yabonye impamyabumenyi ya BA Dramatic Arts yakuye muri kaminuza ya Witwatersrand . Yasoje kandi impamyabumenyi muri firime mu Ishuri ry’Ubuhanzi. 

== Umwuga ==
Muri 2010, yakinnye nka 'Danny Gibson' muri seri ya e.tv ikinamico  ''4 Play: Sex Tips for Girls''. Yakomeje kugira uruhare kugeza muri 2012. Muri 2013, yatsindiye igihembo cya SAFTA Golden Horn igihembo cyumukinnyi mwiza wa serial ''4 Play: Sex Tips for Girls''.  Kuva mu 2006 kugeza 2007, yakinnye nka 'Gabrielle' kuri ''seri zisetsa-ikinamico Izoso Connexion yanyuze'' kuri SABC1. Urukurikirane rwakozwe numugabo we Johnny Barbuzano. Mu mwaka wa 2016, yatorewe igihembo cya SAFTA Golden Horn igihembo cyiza cyagezweho mu myandikire ya ''Kota Life Crisis<ref name="briefly">https://briefly.co.za/80507-tiffany-barbuzano-bio-age-kids-husband-weight-loss-tv-shows-movies-profile.html</ref>'' .  

Ibindi byerekana kumutera imbaraga niSober Companion (2016), Seriously Single (2020) and Still Breathing (2020). Yashinze isosiyete ikora firime 'Localala Productions'. Yagize uruhare mu bitaramo byinshi nka ''Six Inches na Shakers'', ''Macbeth'', ''Othello'' na ''A Midsummer Night Dream'' .  

Tiffany yahise yifatanya n’ikinamico ''Impromptu Zoo'', yakinirwaga kuri Sandton Theatre. ''Yagaragaye kandi mubiganiro'' byinshi bya TV nka ''Quickies'', ''Snitch'', ''Man to Man'', ''Uncle Max'', and ''Binnelanders'' . Usibye gukina, yabaye umwanditsi, kuri seri nyinshi: ''Izoso Connexion'', ''Isidingo'' na ''Scandal'' ndetse no gufata amashusho yikinamico M-Net. Muri 2015, yagaragaye muri seri yikinamico ya BBC ''Wild on Heart'' .  Muri 2017, yatsindiye igihembo cya SAFTA Golden Horn igihembo cy'umukinnyi mwiza kubera uruhare rwe muri televiziyo ''Sober Companion'' <ref name="tvsa">https://www.tvsa.co.za/actors/viewactor.aspx?actorid=6464</ref>. 

Mu ntangiriro za 2020, yatowe na SAFTA Zahabu Ihembe ryiza ryagezweho mu myandikire ya ''Lockdown'' . Muri Kanama 2020, yakinnye muri filime yo gusetsa igitsina ''Seriously Single'' afatanije na Katleho Ramaphakela na Rethabile Ramaphakela . Yasohotse ku ya 31 Nyakanga 2020 kuri Netflix . <ref>http://myheraldmagazine.com/seriously-single-romantic-comedy-premieres-on-netflix-on-31st-july-2020/</ref>

